title: SDSS Remastered.mp4
description:
This is a fully remastered version of the SDSS video from the late 2000's in Full HD (1080p)

It contains over 400,000 galaxies and 100,000 Quasers, with each galaxy unique and the actual photographs captured by various ground based telescopes across the planet.

The SDSS project positioned each object in it's correct position and facing the correct angle.

Feel free to share, this is extremely highly recommended on a large 1080p HDTV for full enjoyment.

Enjoy!
 
:-)
